			<div class="main-card p-12">
				<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
					<div class="space-y-8">
						<div class="faq-item">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">What is Formula Pricing?</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Formula Pricing is an open-source solution for dynamic pricing calculations. It allows you to define complex pricing formulas with variables that can be updated in real-time.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="faq-item">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">How do I get started?</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">You can start by checking out our <a href="/docs" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-700">documentation</a> or trying the <a href="/demo" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-700">live demo</a>. The system is designed to be simple to integrate into your existing applications.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="faq-item">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">What mathematical operations are supported?</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Formula Pricing supports a wide range of mathematical operations including basic arithmetic, functions like min, max, round, and complex conditional logic.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="faq-item">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Can I use it in production?</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Yes! Formula Pricing is designed { "for" } production use with proper error handling, validation, and performance optimization. Check our <a href="/examples" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-700">examples</a> { "for" } real-world use cases.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="faq-item">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Is it open source?</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Yes, Formula Pricing is completely open source. You can find the source code on <a href="https://github.com" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-700">GitHub</a> and contribute to the project.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="faq-item">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">How do I report bugs or request features?</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Please use our GitHub repository to report issues or request new features. We welcome community contributions and feedback.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-12 text-center">
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Still have questions?</p>
						<a href="/" class="button-primary">Back to Home</a>
					</div>
